_sText:
I got bored with the constant poorly-made remakes of ba_jail_electric so I had a go at one myself. 

The jail is set on an island surrounded by water. The water will slowly kill you if you enter it but the two outposts can be reached by the driveable boat.

This map includes:
-A custom sky texture thanks to komaokc
-A 3D skybox
-HDR support
-A driveable boat thanks to NatalyaAF
-18 CT spawn points & 23 T spawn points.
